Odmah!

121
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:04,765
Ti si vojnik.
I tražiš ono što svi vojnici traže.

122
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:06,087
A što je to?

123
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,762
- Časna smrt.

124
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:10,126
Da ti okonča patnju.

125
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,449
Tko kaže da patim?

126
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:18,770
Čovjek koji ima noćne more
svake noći u svom životu, pati.

127
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,680
Jedan dan.

128
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:41,848
Oprostit ću se sa gospodinom
Yashidom, onda se odmah vraćam.

129
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,650
U redu.

130
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:53,609
15 sati. U zavisnosti od vjetra.

131
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:55,850
15 sati?

132
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,360
Ne voliš da letiš?

133
00:16:58,920 --> 00:17:00,445
- Obožavam.

134
